(71, 1, '2018-09-14 07:20:09', '2018-09-14 07:20:09', ' <strong>Tiền lì xì tết 2019</strong>\r\n\r\n2019 Year of the Dog is a remarkable and valued year for all. Repeated once every 60 years in the Chinese calendar, the Year of the Earth Dog is occupying the 11th position in the Chinese Zodiac. The Dog symbolizes such character traits as generous, intelligent, honest and responsible. The Chinese New Year 2018 starts on February 16, 2018 up to February 4, 2019. Year of the Dog Lucky Numbers are 3, 4 and 9, and Lucky Colors are red, green and purple. ', 'Giới Thiệu', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gioi-thieu', '', '', '2018-09-14 07:27:03', '2018-09-14 07:27:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienlixi/?page_id=71', 0, 'page', '', 0),
